5|Consequential Damages Waivers — Major expansion. Added definitional section (Consequential Damages defined term with explicit inclusion of lost profits, AI-specific harms, severability clause). Updated MSA §6.2 to use IDEAL: defined-term approach vs ACCEPTABLE: standard listing approach. Added CA Civil Code §1668 risk note (Apr 2025). Added Brace Industrial Contracting (Del. Ch. 2016) case. Added "lost profits as direct damages in consulting" risk analysis with drafting solution. Added AI-specific consequential damage listing (model poisoning, hallucination losses, regulatory fines, API migration costs). Updated Clause Genome version to 1.6.0.